Company Summary
ServisFirst Bancshares Inc. is a bank holding company. Through its subsidiary, ServisFirst Bank, it provides business and personal financial services. It offers various deposit products; commercial lending products; commercial real estate loans, construction and development loans, and residential real estate loans; and consumer loans.  ServisFirst Bancshares, Inc. is headquartered in Birmingham, Alabama.   

















 




















